                        <article class="post ">
                            <h3 class="uppercase">FÉRIAS</h3><h4>Férias durante o período de calamidade pública: antecipação, pagamento e cancelamento</h4>
                            <ul class="info">
                                <li>
                                    <div class="text date">segunda-feira, 30 de março de 2020</div>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <i class="entyp-pencil-1"></i>
                                    <div class="text">Publicado por CONDUX</div>
                                </li>
                                
                                <li>
                                    <a href="/noticias/?cat=Legisla%E7%E3o+Trabalhista">
                                        <i class="entyp-list-1"></i>
                                        <div class="text">Legislação Trabalhista</div>
                                    </a>
                                </li>
                                
                            </ul>
                            
                            <figure>
                                <img src="https://condux.com.br/site/imgnews/267c.jpg" alt="FÉRIAS"/>
                                
                            </figure>
                            
                            <div class="content">
                            
                                <p>
                                    <strong>
                                       Em decorrência da pandemia de Covid-19, o Governo flexibilizou alguns aspectos das relações de trabalho e agora deu a possibilidade de os empregadores colocarem seus empregados de férias, mesmo que seus períodos aquisitivos não estejam completos.
                                    </strong>
                                </p>
                            <p style="outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: Barlow; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 0.18px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">O Governo Federal, visando amenizar os impactos econ&ocirc;micos provenientes da pandemia de COVID-19, doen&ccedil;a causada pelo novo&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><a class="classtermo" href="https://www.contabeis.com.br/economia/coronavirus/" style="outline: none; color: rgb(52, 142, 157); text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 700; background: none; line-height: inherit; padding: inherit; float: inherit; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">coronavirus,</span></a></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;criou, atrav&eacute;s da&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><a class="external-link" href="http://www.planalto.gov.br/ccivil_03/_ato2019-2022/2020/Mpv/mpv927.htm?rel=outbound?rel=outbound" target="_blank" rel="outbound" style="outline: none; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(52, 142, 157); font-weight: 700; background: none; line-height: inherit; padding: inherit; float: inherit; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">MP 927/2020</span></a></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">, medidas que flexibilizam alguns pontos da legisla&ccedil;&atilde;o trabalhista, como por exemplo a&nbsp;<strong style="outline: none;">possibilidade de antecipa&ccedil;&atilde;o de&nbsp;</strong></span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong style="outline: none;"><a class="classtermo" href="https://www.contabeis.com.br/trabalhista/ferias/" style="outline: none; color: rgb(52, 142, 157); text-decoration-line: none; background: none; line-height: inherit; padding: inherit; float: inherit; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-family: Arial;">f&eacute;rias</span></span></a></strong></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><strong style="outline: none;">&nbsp;individuais</strong>.</span></span></span></p>
<p style="outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 15px 0px 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: Barlow; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 0.18px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">Os outros pontos flexibilizados foram: (1) o&nbsp;teletrabalho; (2) a concess&atilde;o de&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><a class="classtermo" href="https://www.contabeis.com.br/trabalhista/ferias/" style="outline: none; color: rgb(52, 142, 157); text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 700; background: none; line-height: inherit; padding: inherit; float: inherit; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">f&eacute;rias</span></a></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;coletivas; (3) o aproveitamento e a antecipa&ccedil;&atilde;o de feriados; (4) o banco de horas; (5) a suspens&atilde;o de exig&ecirc;ncias administrativas em seguran&ccedil;a e sa&uacute;de no trabalho; (6) o direcionamento do trabalhador para qualifica&ccedil;&atilde;o; e (7) o diferimento do recolhimento do Fundo de Garantia do Tempo de Servi&ccedil;o &ndash;&nbsp;</span></span></span><a class="classtermo" href="https://www.contabeis.com.br/trabalhista/fgts/" style="outline: none; color: rgb(52, 142, 157); text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 700; background: none; line-height: inherit; padding: inherit; float: inherit; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">FGTS.</span></span></span></a></p>
<h3 style="outline: none; margin: 30px 0px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 8px; font-size: 22px; font-weight: normal; display: inline-block; font-family: Barlow; position: relative; line-height: 23px; border-bottom: 3px dotted rgb(238, 238, 238); color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: 0.18px;">&nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"> </span></span></h3>
<h3 style="outline: none; margin: 30px 0px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 8px; font-size: 22px; font-weight: normal; display: inline-block; font-family: Barlow; position: relative; line-height: 23px; border-bottom: 3px dotted rgb(238, 238, 238); color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: 0.18px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">Em tempos normais</span><span style="font-size: 16px;"> </span></h3>
<h3 style="outline: none; margin: 30px 0px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 8px; font-size: 22px; font-weight: normal; display: inline-block; font-family: Barlow; position: relative; line-height: 23px; border-bottom: 3px dotted rgb(238, 238, 238); color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: 0.18px;">&nbsp;</h3>
<p style="outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 15px 0px 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: Barlow; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 0.18px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">Voltando a falar sobre&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><a class="classtermo" href="https://www.contabeis.com.br/trabalhista/ferias/" style="outline: none; color: rgb(52, 142, 157); text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 700; background: none; line-height: inherit; padding: inherit; float: inherit; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">f&eacute;rias,</span></a></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;&eacute; importante registrar inicialmente que hoje, elas est&atilde;o regulamentadas no Cap&iacute;tulo IV da&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><a class="external-link" href="http://www.planalto.gov.br/ccivil_03/decreto-lei/del5452.htm?rel=outbound?rel=outbound" target="_blank" rel="outbound" style="outline: none; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(52, 142, 157); font-weight: 700; background: none; line-height: inherit; padding: inherit; float: inherit; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">Consolida&ccedil;&atilde;o das Leis do Trabalho&nbsp;(CLT)</span></a></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">, com algumas aplica&ccedil;&otilde;es da&nbsp;Conven&ccedil;&atilde;o 132 do Organiza&ccedil;&atilde;o Internacional do Trabalho &ndash; OIT, no Brasil convertida no&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><a class="external-link" href="http://www.planalto.gov.br/ccivil_03/decreto/D3197.htm?rel=outbound?rel=outbound" target="_blank" rel="outbound" style="outline: none; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(52, 142, 157); font-weight: 700; background: none; line-height: inherit; padding: inherit; float: inherit; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">Decreto&nbsp;3.197/1999</span></a></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">.</span></span></span></p>
<p style="outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 15px 0px 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: Barlow; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 0.18px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">Nestes dispositivos legais n&atilde;o h&aacute; qualquer previs&atilde;o para antecipa&ccedil;&atilde;o de&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><a class="classtermo" href="https://www.contabeis.com.br/trabalhista/ferias/" style="outline: none; color: rgb(52, 142, 157); text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 700; background: none; line-height: inherit; padding: inherit; float: inherit; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">f&eacute;rias,</span></a></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;embora tal pr&aacute;tica seja bastante comum no mercado. E neste contexto, conceder&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><a class="classtermo" href="https://www.contabeis.com.br/trabalhista/ferias/" style="outline: none; color: rgb(52, 142, 157); text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 700; background: none; line-height: inherit; padding: inherit; float: inherit; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">f&eacute;rias</span></a></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;a um empregado que n&atilde;o teve o seu per&iacute;odo aquisitivo findado, pode &ndash;&nbsp;<em style="outline: none; font-weight: inherit;">em situa&ccedil;&otilde;es normais&nbsp;</em>&ndash; ocasionar transtornos financeiros e fiscais ao empregador.</span></span></span></p>
<p style="outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 15px 0px 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: Barlow; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 0.18px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">&Eacute; poss&iacute;vel que, em casos de fiscaliza&ccedil;&otilde;es e/ou reclamat&oacute;rias trabalhistas, as&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><a class="classtermo" href="https://www.contabeis.com.br/trabalhista/ferias/" style="outline: none; color: rgb(52, 142, 157); text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 700; background: none; line-height: inherit; padding: inherit; float: inherit; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">f&eacute;rias</span></a></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;antecipadas sejam descaracterizadas e, por sua vez, o per&iacute;odo considerado como uma licen&ccedil;a remunerada, raz&atilde;o pela qual o empregado teria direito a gozar integralmente suas&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><a class="classtermo" href="https://www.contabeis.com.br/trabalhista/ferias/" style="outline: none; color: rgb(52, 142, 157); text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 700; background: none; line-height: inherit; padding: inherit; float: inherit; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">f&eacute;rias</span></a></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;ap&oacute;s a conclus&atilde;o do seu per&iacute;odo aquisitivo.</span></span></span></p>
<h3 style="outline: none; margin: 30px 0px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 8px; font-size: 22px; font-weight: normal; display: inline-block; font-family: Barlow; position: relative; line-height: 23px; border-bottom: 3px dotted rgb(238, 238, 238); color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: 0.18px;">&nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"> </span></span></h3>
<h3 style="outline: none; margin: 30px 0px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 8px; font-size: 22px; font-weight: normal; display: inline-block; font-family: Barlow; position: relative; line-height: 23px; border-bottom: 3px dotted rgb(238, 238, 238); color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: 0.18px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">Em &eacute;poca de pandemia</span><span style="font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></h3>
<p>&nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">Ocorre que, conforme mencionado acima, o Governo flexibilizou alguns aspectos das rela&ccedil;&otilde;es de trabalho e agora deu a possibilidade de os empregadores colocarem seus&nbsp;<strong style="outline: none;">empregados de f&eacute;rias</strong>,&nbsp;<strong style="outline: none;">mesmo que seus per&iacute;odos aquisitivos n&atilde;o estejam completos</strong>.</span></span></span></p>
<p style="outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 15px 0px 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: Barlow; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 0.18px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">&Eacute; importante frisar, no entanto, que essa flexibiliza&ccedil;&atilde;o tem vig&ecirc;ncia apenas durante o estado de calamidade p&uacute;blica reconhecido pelo&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><a class="external-link" href="http://www.planalto.gov.br/ccivil_03/Portaria/DLG6-2020.htm?rel=outbound?rel=outbound" target="_blank" rel="outbound" style="outline: none; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(52, 142, 157); font-weight: 700; background: none; line-height: inherit; padding: inherit; float: inherit; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">Decreto Legislativo n&ordm; 6, de 2020</span></a></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">, conforme disp&otilde;e a&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><a class="external-link" href="http://www.planalto.gov.br/ccivil_03/_ato2019-2022/2020/Mpv/mpv927.htm?rel=outbound?rel=outbound" target="_blank" rel="outbound" style="outline: none; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(52, 142, 157); font-weight: 700; background: none; line-height: inherit; padding: inherit; float: inherit; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">MP 927</span></a></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">.</span></span></span></p>
<p style="outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 15px 0px 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: Barlow; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 0.18px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">De acordo com o artigo 6 da medida provis&oacute;ria mencionada acima, a prerrogativa da decis&atilde;o de antecipar as&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><a class="classtermo" href="https://www.contabeis.com.br/trabalhista/ferias/" style="outline: none; color: rgb(52, 142, 157); text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 700; background: none; line-height: inherit; padding: inherit; float: inherit; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">f&eacute;rias</span></a></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;&eacute; do empregador, que deve informar ao empregado da sua decis&atilde;o com anteced&ecirc;ncia de, no m&iacute;nimo, quarenta e oito horas, por escrito ou por meio eletr&ocirc;nico, com a indica&ccedil;&atilde;o do per&iacute;odo a ser gozado pelo empregado.</span></span></span></p>
<p style="outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 15px 0px 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: Barlow; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 0.18px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">O dispositivo legal pondera que as&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><a class="classtermo" href="https://www.contabeis.com.br/trabalhista/ferias/" style="outline: none; color: rgb(52, 142, 157); text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 700; background: none; line-height: inherit; padding: inherit; float: inherit; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">f&eacute;rias</span></a></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;n&atilde;o poder&atilde;o ser gozadas em per&iacute;odos inferiores a cinco dias corridos e que os trabalhadores que perten&ccedil;am ao grupo de risco do&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><a class="classtermo" href="https://www.contabeis.com.br/economia/coronavirus/" style="outline: none; color: rgb(52, 142, 157); text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 700; background: none; line-height: inherit; padding: inherit; float: inherit; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">coronav&iacute;rus</span></a></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;(covid-19) devem ser priorizados para o gozo de&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><a class="classtermo" href="https://www.contabeis.com.br/trabalhista/ferias/" style="outline: none; color: rgb(52, 142, 157); text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 700; background: none; line-height: inherit; padding: inherit; float: inherit; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">f&eacute;rias,</span></a></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;individuais ou coletivas.</span></span></span></p>
<h3 style="outline: none; margin: 30px 0px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 8px; font-size: 22px; font-weight: normal; display: inline-block; font-family: Barlow; position: relative; line-height: 23px; border-bottom: 3px dotted rgb(238, 238, 238); color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: 0.18px;">&nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"> </span></span></h3>
<h3 style="outline: none; margin: 30px 0px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 8px; font-size: 22px; font-weight: normal; display: inline-block; font-family: Barlow; position: relative; line-height: 23px; border-bottom: 3px dotted rgb(238, 238, 238); color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: 0.18px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">Pagamento das f&eacute;rias</span><span style="font-size: 16px;"> </span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</h3>
<p>&nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">Conforme disp&otilde;e o artigo 8 da&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><a class="external-link" href="http://www.planalto.gov.br/ccivil_03/_ato2019-2022/2020/Mpv/mpv927.htm?rel=outbound" target="_blank" rel="outbound" style="outline: none; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(52, 142, 157); font-weight: 700; background: none; line-height: inherit; padding: inherit; float: inherit; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><strong style="outline: none;">MP 927/20</strong></span></a><span style="font-family: Arial;">, para as&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><a class="classtermo" href="https://www.contabeis.com.br/trabalhista/ferias/" style="outline: none; color: rgb(52, 142, 157); text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 700; background: none; line-height: inherit; padding: inherit; float: inherit; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">f&eacute;rias</span></a></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;concedidas durante&nbsp;o estado de calamidade p&uacute;blica, reconhecido pelo&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><a class="external-link" href="http://www.planalto.gov.br/ccivil_03/Portaria/DLG6-2020.htm?rel=outbound?rel=outbound" target="_blank" rel="outbound" style="outline: none; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(52, 142, 157); font-weight: 700; background: none; line-height: inherit; padding: inherit; float: inherit; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">Decreto Legislativo n&ordm; 6, de 20 de mar&ccedil;o de 2020</span></a></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">, o empregador poder&aacute; optar por efetuar o pagamento do adicional de um ter&ccedil;o de&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><a class="classtermo" href="https://www.contabeis.com.br/trabalhista/ferias/" style="outline: none; color: rgb(52, 142, 157); text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 700; background: none; line-height: inherit; padding: inherit; float: inherit; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">f&eacute;rias</span></a></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;ap&oacute;s sua concess&atilde;o, at&eacute; a data em que &eacute; devido&nbsp;</span></span></span><a class="classtermo" href="https://www.contabeis.com.br/trabalhista/decimo_terceiro_salario/" style="outline: none; color: rgb(52, 142, 157); text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 700; background: none; line-height: inherit; padding: inherit; float: inherit; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">d&eacute;cimo terceiro sal&aacute;rio.</span></span></span></a></p>
<p style="outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 15px 0px 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: Barlow; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 0.18px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">J&aacute; o pagamento da remunera&ccedil;&atilde;o das&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><a class="classtermo" href="https://www.contabeis.com.br/trabalhista/ferias/" style="outline: none; color: rgb(52, 142, 157); text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 700; background: none; line-height: inherit; padding: inherit; float: inherit; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">f&eacute;rias</span></a></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;concedidas em raz&atilde;o do estado de calamidade p&uacute;blica, este poder&aacute; ser efetuado at&eacute; o quinto dia &uacute;til do m&ecirc;s subsequente ao in&iacute;cio do gozo das&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><a class="classtermo" href="https://www.contabeis.com.br/trabalhista/ferias/" style="outline: none; color: rgb(52, 142, 157); text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 700; background: none; line-height: inherit; padding: inherit; float: inherit; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">f&eacute;rias.</span></a></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;O prazo previsto no artigo 145 da&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><a class="classtermo" href="https://www.contabeis.com.br/trabalhista/clt/" style="outline: none; color: rgb(52, 142, 157); text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 700; background: none; line-height: inherit; padding: inherit; float: inherit; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">CLT,</span></a></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;de dois dias antes do in&iacute;cio, n&atilde;o ser&aacute; aplicado.</span></span></span></p>
<p style="outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 15px 0px 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: Barlow; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 0.18px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">Caso haja rescis&atilde;o de contrato de trabalho de algum profissional cuja remunera&ccedil;&atilde;o de&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><a class="classtermo" href="https://www.contabeis.com.br/trabalhista/ferias/" style="outline: none; color: rgb(52, 142, 157); text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 700; background: none; line-height: inherit; padding: inherit; float: inherit; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">f&eacute;rias</span></a></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;ou do ter&ccedil;o constitucional ainda n&atilde;o tenha sido paga em sua totalidade, o valor deve compor as verbas rescis&oacute;rias.</span></span></span></p>
<h3 style="outline: none; margin: 30px 0px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 8px; font-size: 22px; font-weight: normal; display: inline-block; font-family: Barlow; position: relative; line-height: 23px; border-bottom: 3px dotted rgb(238, 238, 238); color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: 0.18px;">&nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"> </span></span></h3>
<h3 style="outline: none; margin: 30px 0px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 8px; font-size: 22px; font-weight: normal; display: inline-block; font-family: Barlow; position: relative; line-height: 23px; border-bottom: 3px dotted rgb(238, 238, 238); color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: 0.18px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">Do cancelamento de f&eacute;rias</span><span style="font-size: 16px;"> </span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</h3>
<p>&nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">Em se tratando de colaboradores da &aacute;rea de sa&uacute;de ou daqueles que desempenhem fun&ccedil;&otilde;es essenciais, a&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><a class="external-link" href="http://www.planalto.gov.br/ccivil_03/_ato2019-2022/2020/Mpv/mpv927.htm?rel=outbound?rel=outbound" target="_blank" rel="outbound" style="outline: none; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(52, 142, 157); font-weight: 700; background: none; line-height: inherit; padding: inherit; float: inherit; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">MP 927/20</span></a></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">, concede aos empregadores a permiss&atilde;o para que, durante&nbsp;o estado de calamidade p&uacute;blica&nbsp;, possa suspender as&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><a class="classtermo" href="https://www.contabeis.com.br/trabalhista/ferias/" style="outline: none; color: rgb(52, 142, 157); text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: 700; background: none; line-height: inherit; padding: inherit; float: inherit; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">f&eacute;rias</span></a></span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;ou licen&ccedil;as n&atilde;o remuneradas dos profissionais, desde que a sua decis&atilde;o seja comunicada de maneira formal, por escrito ou por meio eletr&ocirc;nico, preferencialmente com anteced&ecirc;ncia de quarenta e oito horas. </span></span></span></p>
<p style="outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 15px 0px 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: Barlow; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 0.18px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-family: Arial;">Fonte: Site Cont&aacute;beis</span></span></span></p>
<p style="outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 15px 0px 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: Barlow; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 0.18px;">&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
                            </div>
                            
